          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "enable_image": false,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<h4><em>Great product, it really works</em></h4><p>\"I was skeptical at first, but after using it 2x a week for 3 weeks, I really felt a difference. I had relief from all the itching. The product really works for me, so it's 100% worth the price\"</p><p>Cath L. from Quezon City</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "enable_video": false,
            "video_link": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_9VUPq3SxOc"
          }
        },
        "857bc470-b409-4c29-9d8c-cb5f009efcbd": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "enable_image": false,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<h4><em>Worth it!</em></h4><p>\"I've been struggling with dandruff for years and Davines' Purifying line is the only that worked for me. Despite being more expensive than other brands, it's worth it!\"</p><p>Mon L. from Quezon City</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "enable_video": false,
            "video_link": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_9VUPq3SxOc"
          }
        },
        "94b16482-c0a4-424f-9321-bd9824f597e2": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "enable_image": false,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<h4><em>Worth it. Effective against Scalp Psoriasis</em></h4><p>\"I've tried every product you can think of for my scalp psoriasis. But this is the only one I found to be effective! With consistent use, I am (mostly) flake free :) I used it everyday for the first 1-2 weeks then I started alternating it with a gentle shampoo. Highly recommend!\"</p><p>Jamie from Caloocan City</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "enable_video": false,
            "video_link": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_9VUPq3SxOc"
          }
        }
      },
